NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Next, instead of doubling, Roberta should bid 2S. In general, you should always prefer to overcall a 5 card major to doubling. In fact even if it goes 1 of a minor, and you are 5/4 or 4/5 in the majors you should prefer to bid your 5 card suit to doubling. It makes it easier for partner to compete. |
