NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Therefore, the 4-4 fits are not always desirable. For close games they are, because you might need that extra trick in the long 5 or 6 card suit. But, in games which are clear cut, the 5-3, or 9 card fit is usually safer.|
