^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Let us first discuss why Jana should consider slam, even though on this hand she should only make 5. Let us count her Bergen Points. She has 17 HCP, plus 1 length point, = 18 starting points. Once Darlene raises hearts, she can add 2 for the singleton and 1 for the 4 card diamond suit, which gives her 21. With  Darlene's 12, they are in slam range. And indeed if Darlene had the Q of spades in addition to what she had, it does make slam. I am not saying Jana should bid slam, but she should consider it.|
